::Magmatron/Bobertron::

    "That insect will let us spy on the bot who is trying to spy on us." 
Magmatron explained to Bobertron. "It will also infect all others of it's 
kind with the same virus. So if he destroys all the spys in the base we will 
have nothing to worry about, and if he doesn't...I give it five megacycles 
before every bug in this place is under my control."
